{"id":481,"date":"2019-03-01T22:24:11","date_gmt":"2019-03-01T22:24:11","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/adamhorne.com\/?page_id=481"},"modified":"2019-03-06T19:08:31","modified_gmt":"2019-03-06T19:08:31","slug":"amazon-alexa-future-world-trivia","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/adamhorne.com\/amazon-alexa-future-world-trivia\/","title":{"rendered":"Amazon Alexa: Future World Trivia"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<h2>How well do you know the future?<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed-youtube alignfull wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"360\" src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/8d35gY6cb6Q?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen><\/iframe>\n<\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"235\" src=\"https:\/\/adamhorne.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/Alexa-Future-World-Trivia-Cargo-Image-1024x235.png\" alt=\"Amazon Alexa: Future World Trivia is an Amazon Alexa Skill that I made to learn more about how a voice interface can work. I was responsible for the concept, writing and javascript development.\" class=\"wp-image-482\" srcset=\"https:\/\/adamhorne.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/Alexa-Future-World-Trivia-Cargo-Image-1024x235.png 1024w, https:\/\/adamhorne.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/Alexa-Future-World-Trivia-Cargo-Image-300x69.png 300w, https:\/\/adamhorne.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/Alexa-Future-World-Trivia-Cargo-Image-768x177.png 768w, https:\/\/adamhorne.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/Alexa-Future-World-Trivia-Cargo-Image-1568x360.png 1568w, https:\/\/adamhorne.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/Alexa-Future-World-Trivia-Cargo-Image.png 1649w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns has-2-columns\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\">\n<p>As the world moves from visual interfaces, to voice interfaces, where do you even begin to learn this stuff?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>You\n start by developing a simple voice-based trivia game for the Amazon \nEcho. Introducing Future World Trivia, a fun game that tests on you \nhistory that hasn&#8217;t happened yet.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\">\n<p>This was a perfect introduction on how Amazon Lambara can work with \nthe Alexa Skills Kit API. Despite a whole lot of debugging, hair pulling\n and rewriting of code and copy\u2026<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can <a href=\"https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/dp\/B073T6Z223\">enable the skill on your Amazon Echo here.<\/a><br><br>And check out the Node.js source code on <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/github.com\/adamghorne\/AlexaFutureWorldTrivia\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">GitHub<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\/\/A \ud83d\udcac&nbsp;<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>How well do you know the future? As the world moves from visual interfaces, to voice interfaces, where do you even begin to learn this stuff? You start by developing a simple voice-based trivia game for the Amazon Echo. Introducing Future World Trivia, a fun game that tests on you history that hasn&#8217;t happened yet. [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/adamhorne.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/481"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/adamhorne.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/adamhorne.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/adamhorne.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/adamhorne.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=481"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"https:\/\/adamhorne.com\/wp-js